ice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-11T23:10:15Z to 2025-06-11T23:20:15Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-11 23:10:15+00:00 to 2025-06-11 23:20:15+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2", "emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["adservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "cartservice-0", "paymentservice-1", "frontend-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["cartservice-1", "paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "cpu_usage", "error_ratio", "node_cpu_usage_rate", "node_filesystem_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "pod_processes", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [],\n  \"hypotheses\": []\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "我们找到了故障期间的显著异常指标数据，并根据它制定了分析结果。以下是对异常调用链和资源瓶颈的分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_filesystem_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_processes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate 在故障期间显著增加，从25.2增至67.73，指示该节点的文件系统资源使用快速增长可能导致系统故障。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_median: 25.2, fault_median: 67.73, change_ratio: 0.9152\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice-0的rrt_max在故障期间显著增加，从7816.99增至31172.59，指示服务响应时间显著拖慢可能影响性能。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_p99: 7816.99, fault_p99: 31172.59, change_ratio: 1.198\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes 和 pod_cpu_usage 指标显示redis-cart-0异常，pod_processes 变化从正常值1.0到故障期间仍为1.0但有过程指标变化，pod_cpu_usage从故障前忽略不计到故障期间显示指标，可能指示异步处理或任务积压。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes normal_p99: 2.0, fault_p99: 1.0, change_ratio: 0.6667; pod_cpu_usage normal_p99: 0.09, fault_p99: 0.05, change_ratio: 0.5273\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过该分析，我们发现问题来源于多个组件资源使用上的显著变化，特别是节点文件系统使用率、服务响应时间和资源使用异常。我们建议对这几个组件进行详细检查以确定具体的修复措施。", "trace_analysis_findings": "调用链数据已成功载入。我们现在进行分析，以找出异常调用链，并识别延迟瓶颈及可能的根因。\n\n### 异常调用链数据分析\n我们在事故发生期间的异常调用链中发现以下显著延迟和异常情况：\n\n1. **ShippingService**:\n   - 请求 `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote` 从 `frontend` 到 `shippingservice` 平均耗时在异常时段增加到正常平均值的 **1.64倍** (330.25 vs 201.39)，此异常发生 **2次**。\n\n2. **Redis**:\n   - 请求 `HMSET` 在 `cartservice-0` 的异常时耗时增加到正常平均值的 **6倍** (9442.0 vs 1573.06)，此异常发生 **1次**。\n\n3. **CheckoutService**:\n   - 请求 `hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation` 在 `checkoutservice` 中的平均耗时增加到正常平均值的 **3.91倍** (80592.0 vs 20617.15)，此异常发生 **1次**。\n\n4. **CartService**:\n   - 请求 `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 在 `cartservice-2` 中的平均耗时增加到正常平均值的 **4.58倍** (10584.56 vs 2310.18)，此异常发生 **1次**。\n\n5. **ShippingService**:\n   - 请求 `hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder` 在 `shippingservice` 中的平均耗时增加到正常平均值的 **6倍** (75773.0 vs 13942.70)，此异常发生 **1次**。\n\n### 延迟和错误分析\n\n- **Redis**在`cartservice-0`和`cartservice-2`上显示显著延迟，这可能表示数据获取和保存过程中出现瓶颈。\n- **CheckoutService**进行邮件确认时也出现了显著的延迟。\n- **CartService**获取购物车信息的请求也显著增加，可能表明在`CartService`组件中存在数据处理或网络延迟问题。\n\n### JSON 输出示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"cartservice-0->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HMSET 超过正常平均值延迟 6倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation 超过正常平均值延迟 3.91倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetCart 超过正常平均值延迟 4.58倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析为初始结果，后续可能需要进一步验证这些组件的配置和状态以确定详细根因。"}
